&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own Typeform’s editorial roadmap and calendar across newsletters, blogs, reports, thought leadership, and long form storytelling&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead editorial direction across campaigns, product storytelling, research content, and executive thought leadership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as the primary editor and final quality reviewer for key written content across the business&lt;/li&gt;
